    public final class Dictionary<V>
extends Map<java.lang.String,V>
    This collection class is a convenience class that implements a Map whose keys are always of type String. The implementation dynamically scales up and down the size of the underlying data structures as the number elements changes over time.
    Author:
    Derk Norton

        public Dictionary(java.lang.String[] keys,

        This constructor creates a new dictionary using the specified key and value arrays. The number of keys must equal the number of values or an exception is thrown.
